Step 1: Nuclear Reset 
Before we start fresh, we must kill any "zombie" containers, networks, or old files that are  causing the Conflict errors. 

Bash 
# Stop and remove all containers 
docker stop data-logger sensor-sim 2>/dev/null 
docker rm data-logger sensor-sim 2>/dev/null



# Remove the network 
docker network rm sensor-net 2>/dev/null



# Clear folder in our Main EC Labs Folder to start fresh 
mkdir Expt3 

